Package org.netbeans.swing.dirchooser

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DelegatingChooserUI
    Placeholder ComponentUI that just delegates to other FileChooserUIs based on what selection mode is set in JFileChooser.
    DirectoryCellEditor
    A simple tree cell editor helper used to properly display a node while in editing mode.
    DirectoryChooserUI
    An implementation of a customized filechooser.
    DirectoryNode
    A directory tree node.
    DirectoryNode.FileNameComparator
    Compares files ignoring case sensitivity
    FileCompletionPopup
    A class that handles the "File Name:" text field auto-completion drop-down selection list.
    InputBlocker
    Blocks user's input when FileChooser is busy.
    Module
    Registers the directory chooser in NetBeans.
